1. Display on LCD a clock (HH-MM-SS)
2. Each XX time you should save the measurement
3. You should be able to change the clock
  - rotaty knobs (directions: L,R)
    - no activity on RK - clock remains on its own pace
    - you touched RK - then HH [are blinking] and you are able to change it (L,R)
                     - after 5 seconds switch to MM
                     - SS are zeroed after changing time
                     - after next 5 sec of incativity got ot normal mode
4. Pick a asensor and wake an interface

